				fill="url(#paint0_linear_1805_24383)"></path>
			<defs>
				<linearGradient
					id="paint0_linear_1805_24383"
					x1="247.358"
					y1="0"
					x2="247.358"
					y2="622.479"
					gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
				>
					<stop stop-opacity="0.9"></stop>
					<stop offset="1" stop-opacity="0.2"></stop>
				</linearGradient>
			</defs>
		</svg>
		<h1><span class="text-gradient">Secret</span> area !</h1>
		
        <div class="instructions" id="linkDiv" style="cursor: pointer;">
            <img src="https://www.nautiljon.com/images/perso/00/00/sakurajima_mai_17600.webp" class="myqueen">
            <h2>Sakurajima Mai</h2>
            <text>Probably the most mature character in this list.<br/>
              She is a notable actress/model and a third year at Minegahara High School.
            </text>
          </div>
          <Card2
            title="My Anime List"
            href="https://myanimelist.net/profile/Leclowndu93150"
            />
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
			<Card
                href="https://myanimelist.net/character/161286/Chizuru_Ichinose?q=mizuhara%20chizuru&cat=character"
                image="https://www.nautiljon.com/images/perso/00/65/mizuhara_chizuru_19556.webp?1681834490"
				title="Mizuhara Chizuru/Ichinose Chizuru"
				body="She is a college student at Nerima University who is majoring in Literature. She currently lives in Room 204 of Royal Hills Nerima. She works as a rental girlfriend for an agency called Diamond under the alias Chizuru Mizuhara (水原 千鶴)."
                />
            <Card
                href="https://oshinoko.fandom.com/wiki/Kana_Arima"
                image="https://www.nautiljon.com/images/perso/00/91/arima_kana_21419.webp"
                title="Arima Kana"
                body="Formerly a prodigy child actress, Kana Arima lost most of her footing in the entertainment industry due to the poor reputation she garnered for herself on set during her grade school years. Though her attitude has greatly reformed by the present day, her image as merely a washed-up child actor continues to hamper her efforts."
            />
            <Card
                href="https://myanimelist.net/character/163271/Tsukasa_Yuzaki"
                image="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1323294613617037312/ISPirPjS_400x400.jpg"
                title="Yuzaki Tsukasa"
                body="Nasa Yuzaki's wife. She saved Nasa from getting hit by a truck during a snowy night, and he confessed to her at that moment, taken aback by her beauty. Tsukasa agreed to go out with Nasa on the condition that they get married."
                text="Not much is known about Tsukasa's past. She has a strong love for movies, otaku culture, and of course her husband. Her maiden name is Tsukuyomi (月読)."
                />
            <Card
                image="https://images.genius.com/fe17f85f150c87b2ccd7612d7a1456b5.507x507x1.jpg"
                title="Natsukawa Aika"
                body="She is the main female protagonist of the Yumemiru Danshi wa Genjitsushugisha series."
                text=" She is the beautiful girl in her class who is bewildered by Wataru Sajou's sudden change in attitude and her own feelings of confusion."
                href="https://myanimelist.net/character/202840/Aika_Natsukawa"
                />
			<Card
				image="https://www.nautiljon.com/images/perso/00/17/sakuranomiya_maika_15871.webp"
				title="Sakuranomiya Maika"
				body="She is a 16-year-old girl who despite having a positive and cheerful personality, unintentionally gains a sadistic look in her eyes whenever she smiles. This look catches the attention of Dino who scouts her to be the sadistic girl waitress at Cafe Stile. Despite being told that the customers like being treated badly, her worry about how she is treating customers gets the better of her, causing her to snap into an apologetic personality as soon as they have left. "
				href="https://blend-s.fandom.com/wiki/Maika_Sakuranomiya"
			/>
			<Card
				image="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/c0/60/d4/c060d48afe925d212d125776d716d131.jpg"
				title="Gotō Hitori/Bocchi-chan"
				body="An extremely timid and introverted first-year student in high school. She is in charge of the responsibility of playing the lead guitar for Kessoku Band. She aspires to perform in a band that could showcase even a reserved girl's talent, hence she began playing the guitar. Although her skill is the real deal, she struggles to exhibit it proficiently in a band or in front of an audience. Additionally, she possesses a habit of saying 'Ah' before she speaks."
				href="https://bocchi-the-rock.fandom.com/wiki/Hitori_Gotoh"
			/>
			

		</ul>
		<Card2
            title="The Quintessential Quintuplets"
            href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Quintessential_Quintuplets"
            />
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid2">
			<Card 
			image="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/E8XbcivXsAUDjM7.jpg"
			title="Nakano Yotsuba"
			/>
			<Card 
			image="https://avatarfiles.alphacoders.com/323/323109.jpg"
			title="Nakano Ichika"
			/>
			<Card 
			image="https://i.redd.it/peahlzqaetl61.png"
			title="Nakano Itsuki"
			/>
			<Card 
			image="https://thicc-af.mywaifulist.moe/waifus/miku-nakano-the-quintessential-quintuplets/TUL6HSyA3N051ixzute6Uh6pFx3A1z6AHwtrb1CE.jpg?class=thumbnail"
			title="Nakano Miku"
			/>
			<Card 
			image="https://i.pinimg.com/1200x/64/f7/83/64f783fd3f3c154061da8f15379a920e.jpg"
			title="Nakano Nino"
			/>

		</ul>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient2);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 300%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
    .instructions {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light2), 25%);
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(var(--accent2), 66%), rgba(var(--accent2), 33%));
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center; /* Center the content horizontally */
	}

	.myqueen {
		display: block;
		margin: 0 auto; /* Center the image horizontally */
		max-width: 100%;
        border-radius: 2%;
        max-height: 400px;
	}
	
    .instructions img {
		max-width: 100%; /* To ensure the image doesn't exceed its container */
	}

    .instructions strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light2));
	}

    .instructions h2{
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
	}


	.link-card-grid2 {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap; /* Prevent wrapping to new lines */
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 10px auto;
    overflow-x: auto; /* Add horizontal scroll for small screens */
}

.link-card-grid2 > * {
    flex: 0 0 auto; /* Disable shrinking to prevent cards from being hidden */
    min-width: calc(20ch - 1rem); /* Adjust minimum width as needed */
    width: calc(20ch - 1rem); /* Set the width to the same as minimum width */
}

	/* Add hover animation for .link-card2 */
	.link-card2:hover,
	.link-card2:focus-within {
		background-position: 0;
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		transition: background-position 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1), background-image 1.5s ease-out;
	}

	.link-card2:hover h2,
	.link-card2:focus-within h2 {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		transition: color 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
	}

	.quintuplets{
		text-align: center;
	}

</style>

<script>
    const linkDiv = document.getElementById('linkDiv');
    const link = 'https://aobuta.fandom.com/wiki/Mai_Sakurajima';
    linkDiv.addEventListener('click', () => {
      window.location.href = link;
    });
</script>